# Marketplace Pipeline — Core Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` before non-trivial changes.

## Stack

Python 3.11 · Pydantic v2 · httpx · tenacity · pytest · ruff

## Business invariants

- Partial collection (< target) is success when category exhausted
- Parser errors → graceful degradation, never crash on partial data
- CRM idempotency: SHA-256(title+description), store at `data/crm_idempotency.json`
- `MOCK_PARSER` is env-only (no separate mock HTTP server)
- Segment «Стандарт» classified but not sent to CRM

## Code style

- External HTTP only through `HttpClient`
- Settings via `config.Settings`, never raw `os.environ` in modules
- New IO schemas as Pydantic models in `models.py`
- Line length 100, ruff clean

## Before commit

```bash
ruff check src tests && pytest
```

Coverage must stay ≥95%.
